Good.

259
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:12,661
But...

260
00:22:12,661 --> 00:22:14,330
Why the hurry?

261
00:22:14,330 --> 00:22:18,038
C'mon, she was a young widow... With kids!

262
00:22:18,038 --> 00:22:20,729
Plus, the Army stopped paying her his pension...

263
00:22:20,729 --> 00:22:23,649
They want to 'investigate' him!

264
00:22:23,789 --> 00:22:26,851
She needed someone to support her...

265
00:22:27,970 --> 00:22:30,929
How'd she agree so easily?

266
00:22:31,453 --> 00:22:33,304
How couldn't she?

267
00:22:33,304 --> 00:22:35,503
She had no choice.

268
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:43,168
Didn't she love your brother?

269
00:22:43,168 --> 00:22:45,408
Perhaps she did, perhaps she didn't...

270
00:22:45,408 --> 00:22:47,498
But love stands no chance...

271
00:22:47,498 --> 00:22:50,869
When you're struggling to make ends meet...

272
00:22:50,869 --> 00:22:53,840
And your stomach starts growling...

273
00:22:53,840 --> 00:22:57,781
She was in dire need, yes, she was...

274
00:23:05,570 --> 00:23:08,080
It's getting late... Where's Vishal?

275
00:23:08,080 --> 00:23:10,171
I'll have a look...

276
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:23,809
Congratulations on Sarah's admission.

277
00:23:23,939 --> 00:23:26,698
Sherali's dream is coming true!

278
00:23:26,698 --> 00:23:29,249
The Lord has been kind...

279
00:23:29,329 --> 00:23:32,519
Sarah's worked hard, despite everyth --

280
00:23:32,519 --> 00:23:35,120
You've worked hard too.

281
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:41,490
After Sherali's death... In her place, most girls won't even be able to sit an exam...

282
00:23:41,830 --> 00:23:45,600
Aye... Just pray things go on fine...

283
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:48,830
I always pray for you...

284
00:23:48,830 --> 00:23:52,288
You're the only ones with Mum and Dad...

285
00:23:52,848 --> 00:23:54,590
Amna...

286
00:23:54,810 --> 00:23:58,668
I asked for something...

287
00:23:59,398 --> 00:24:02,738
Zafar's been asking me about it...

288
00:24:09,840 --> 00:24:11,461
Ayesha...

289
00:24:11,803 --> 00:24:13,868
I'm sorry...

290
00:24:15,340 --> 00:24:17,899
For what?

291
00:24:18,380 --> 00:24:22,868
I can't help you... Sorry...

292
00:24:24,850 --> 00:24:26,568
I --

293
00:24:27,188 --> 00:24:31,109
I thought about it a lot...

294
00:24:31,340 --> 00:24:35,440
This money... Is for my kids... And --

295
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:37,870
It's not like we said it's ours.

296
00:24:37,870 --> 00:24:42,488
We don't have a right over it... We're just borrowing it in times of need...

297
00:24:42,488 --> 00:24:45,740
I understand, Ayesha...

298
00:24:45,740 --> 00:24:48,140
But...

299
00:24:48,140 --> 00:24:51,461
I can't give you any of it...

300
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:55,138
Why? You're the only one who can give it away...

301
00:24:55,138 --> 00:24:57,999
Yes... I can...

302
00:24:57,999 --> 00:25:00,580
But I won't...

303
00:25:01,100 --> 00:25:04,248
Did you tell Mum and Dad?

304
00:25:06,580 --> 00:25:08,398
Yes.

305
00:25:09,021 --> 00:25:12,262
And -- They're with you on this?

306
00:25:12,262 --> 00:25:13,893
No.

307
00:25:13,983 --> 00:25:16,190
I'm turning you down myself...

308
00:25:16,190 --> 00:25:19,238
As the mother of Sherali's kids...

309
00:25:19,890 --> 00:25:21,686
Ayesha...

310
00:25:21,686 --> 00:25:30,522
You were and always will be their Aunt...

311
00:25:30,522 --> 00:25:32,137
But I think...

312
00:25:32,137 --> 00:25:36,767
Sherali helped you all he could while he was here...

313
00:25:36,767 --> 00:25:39,730
But...

314
00:25:39,730 --> 00:25:42,299
No longer...

315
00:26:01,170 --> 00:26:02,990
Vishal here yet?

316
00:26:02,990 --> 00:26:04,771
No.

317
00:27:08,360 --> 00:27:09,549
Vishal!

318
00:27:09,549 --> 00:27:11,290
What happened?

319
00:27:18,660 --> 00:27:19,959
Vishal?

320
00:27:19,959 --> 00:27:21,270
Vishal!

321
00:27:21,270 --> 00:27:22,808
Hey!

322
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:30,000
Vishal! Wait!
