323
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:32,000
Translation: Fajr Aurangzeb © ZEE5

324
00:27:32,130 --> 00:27:34,151
Wow, you're lovely...

325
00:27:34,151 --> 00:27:36,182
And you're... Average...

326
00:27:36,182 --> 00:27:39,960
And aye... I'm lovely. So?

327
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:43,810
Why don't you apply to the Army?

328
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:47,060
I don't want to marry a soldier, Vishal...

329
00:27:47,060 --> 00:27:52,788
Because I don't want to die everyday like your Mum and mine...

330
00:27:52,956 --> 00:27:57,951
A uniform makes lions of men...

